The paper proposes an algorithm for autonomous vehicles to navigate safely in urban environments, which involves processing sensor data and making predictions based on road layouts. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
